These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, pumpkin
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, surfing
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person eating pumpkin##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | pumpkin   | cabbage  |
| Sport   | tennis | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, onion
2 different pets are kept: pony, ferret
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the pony is not the person eating onion##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | broccoli | onion      |
| Pet    | pony  | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
