.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
There 2 different types of food: mango, cauliflower
2 different pets are kept: rat, horse
1. the person eating cauliflower is not the owner of the rat##6
2. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2      |
| Food   | mango  | cauliflower |
| Pet    | rat | horse    |

