.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, analyst
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, bird
1. the freelancer is in an odd position##4
2. the freelancer is not the owner of the bird##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | freelancer | analyst |
| Pet   | hedgehog       | bird       |

